Self-Improvement - Theres more than one way to climb trees.

I have had the habit of recording my progress in whatever I did, no matter how redundant. And often I would try and break those records. After all, self-improvement is what life is all about, whether it's academics or sports. But even though I'd try and best myself whenever I could, I felt I wasn't pushing myself to the limit.

That was until I switched school, and joined Podar. 
